TableContextTimeStampAfterTable: {134=A short-lived but interesting radio show focused on GNU/Linux, BSD and Free Software, broadcast from Brooklyn, NY from June 2002 to June 2003. One of several projects run by the New York Linux Scene, a group dedicated to spreading the word of Free Software to the city that never sleeps. The NYLXS website is at http://www.nylxs.com.}
